	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey,
<br />
<br />Is it just as simple as adding the battery to the spot on the PCB to make a metroid PCB use the battery to make say FF2e or is there more to it?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
