	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's as simple as adding battery, resistors and diodes where there is empty slots for them. Unfotrunately there is no battery with the dimentions that matches the one in Nintendo games in the market, so you'll have to be tricky to make one hold on the board and make reliable contact.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
